{"tid":2131110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［FB] HK Frxxt 專門店 寄爛生果 再要告我誹謗","createTime":"2020-07-29T15:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T15:07:58.000Z","uid":21122,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ac54b44c6df55532a8bb5b44136f7273b05fc2de","tid":2131110,"uid":21122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"話說係fb 香港水果 專賣日本水果嘅專門店<br />\n之前訂過一次冇事<br />\n和歌山 水蜜桃 一箱賣 $596<br />\n<br />\n今次再訂<br />\n講好左上星期六送<br />\n然後話派送有問題 要延遲到今個星期二<br />\n<br />\n今日速遞送黎一箱爛桃，箱面寫住紀之川<br />\n每一粒桃都爛晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後包裝 同 上一次都唔同<br />\n上次就寫住<span class=\"x-large\"> 和歌山</span> ，今日個箱寫 <span class=\"x-large\">紀之川</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">CS 堅持 水果係唔會換，<br />\n$596 爛到一粒都食唔到 都係貴客自理</span><br />\n個包裝同大陸野冇乜分別<br />\n<br />\n仲話：紀之川水蜜桃就係和歌山水蜜桃<br />\n完全解釋唔到包裝點解唔一樣<br />\n<br />\n不過是撚旦 <br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"purple\"><span class=\"x-large\">但你賣爛水果就唔關和歌山事啦掛</span><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"x-large\"> CS 金句： 咁d桃甜唔甜呀？</span></span><br />\n最後 仲話我誹謗佢<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線 影晒相 有晒單 係你鋪頭寄幾箱爛水果<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">你話我誹謗緊你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個packaging 已經心知不妙</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bps6nUx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBps6nUx.jpg&h=54c89384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"green\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後一打開</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRsx2UY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRsx2UY.jpg&h=6de2106b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">一撚定甜啦</span>"},{"pid":"41f6ed58